Interface TurtleBinary

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Invokable, IterableInvokable, TurtleIterable
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface TurtleBinary
extends IterableInvokable, TurtleIterable
    This interface allows for commands with 2 arguments that operate on each turtle
